caption.p: Volcano Plot shows differentially abundant proteins in CV-PTC and FV-PTC. The plot constructed using −log 10 (p value) against the log 2 (fold change).The non-axial vertical lines represent ±1-fold change. The non-axial horizontal lines show p = 0.05 and p = 0.0005 (Benjamini-Hochberg corrected P value).
